    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a meticulously maintained E46 M3, a pinnacle of German engineering featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a linear 333 hp. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical mechanical addressals include a reinforced rear subframe and a recent VANOS service, ensuring structural rigidity and timing accuracy. The suspension geometry remains tight, currently running a refreshed set of bushings and performance-tuned dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical components are optimized for peak lateral acceleration and throttle response. This is a true driver\u2019s spec, prioritizing powertrain health and chassis dynamics.",
